      "type": "text",
      "data": "<div style=\"position: relative;\"><div class=\"exp-content-block\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; margin-top: 40px;\"><h2 class=\"exp-content-head\" style=\"margin: 40px 0px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 400; line-height: 24px; font-family: 微软雅黑; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(214, 214, 216);\">方法/步骤</h2><div class=\"exp-content-body\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-top: 5px;\"><ol class=\"exp-conent-orderlist\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; clear: both;\"><li class=\"exp-content-list list-item-1\" style=\"margin: 20px 0px 0px 17px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 35px; display: block; position: relative; min-height: 31px; border-left-width: 2px; border-left-style: dotted; border-left-color: rgb(228, 228, 228);\"><div class=\"list-icon\" style=\"width: 32px; height: 32px; position: absolute; left: -18px; top: 0px; color: rgb(238, 255, 238); text-align: center; line-height: 32px; background-image: url(http://img.baidu.com/img/iknow/exp/global/step_ol_bg.png); visibility: hidden; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\"></div><div class=\"content-list-text\"><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">经常遇见在阅读代码时，出现许多空白行，当你使用类似于indentLine的VIM插件时，在空白行就会出现断裂，十分影响阅读。如图：</p></div><div class=\"content-list-media\"><div class=\"content-list-image clearfix\" style=\"zoom: 1; position: relative; padding: 10px 0px;\"><a class=\"exp-image-wraper\" href=\"http://jingyan.baidu.com/album/a378c960911053b32928305b.html?picindex=1\" log=\"type:20150831,pos:enter_step,expGroup:G0\" target=\"_self\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(45, 100, 179); position: relative; display: block; float: left;\"><img class=\"exp-image-default\" alt=\"VIM删除空白行\" src=\"quiver-image-url/625ACD8E67B44AE25FF5E072C80D2BCF.png\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block;\" width=\"375\" height=\"285\"><span class=\"exp-album-enter-mask\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 0px; right: 0px; top: 0px; bottom: 0px; background-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); opacity: 0; cursor: pointer;\"></span></a></div></div></li><li class=\"exp-content-list list-item-2\" style=\"margin: 1px 0px 0px 17px; padding: 45px 0px 0px 35px; display: block; position: relative; min-height: 31px; border-left-width: 2px; border-left-style: dotted; border-left-color: rgb(228, 228, 228);\"><div class=\"list-icon\" style=\"width: 32px; height: 32px; position: absolute; left: -18px; top: 43px; color: rgb(238, 255, 238); text-align: center; line-height: 32px; background-image: url(http://img.baidu.com/img/iknow/exp/global/step_ol_bg.png); visibility: hidden; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\"></div><div class=\"content-list-text\"><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">在命令状态下输入：</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">：g/^\\s*$/d</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">如图：</p></div><div class=\"content-list-media\"><div class=\"content-list-image clearfix\" style=\"zoom: 1; position: relative; padding: 10px 0px;\"><a class=\"exp-image-wraper\" href=\"http://jingyan.baidu.com/album/a378c960911053b32928305b.html?picindex=2\" log=\"type:20150831,pos:enter_step,expGroup:G0\" target=\"_self\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(45, 100, 179); position: relative; display: block; float: left;\"><img class=\"exp-image-default\" alt=\"VIM删除空白行\" src=\"quiver-image-url/BED51D853A725D0A20D383BA10195571.png\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block;\" width=\"375\" height=\"94\"><span class=\"exp-album-enter-mask\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 0px; right: 0px; top: 0px; bottom: 0px; background-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); opacity: 0; cursor: pointer;\"></span></a></div></div></li><li class=\"exp-content-list list-item-3\" style=\"margin: 1px 0px 0px 17px; padding: 45px 0px 0px 35px; display: block; position: relative; min-height: 31px; border-left-width: 2px; border-left-style: dotted; border-left-color: rgb(228, 228, 228);\"><div class=\"list-icon\" style=\"width: 32px; height: 32px; position: absolute; left: -18px; top: 43px; color: rgb(238, 255, 238); text-align: center; line-height: 32px; background-image: url(http://img.baidu.com/img/iknow/exp/global/step_ol_bg.png); visibility: hidden; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\"></div><div class=\"content-list-text\"><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">:g 代表在全文档范围内</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">^代表行的开始</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\\s*代表空白字符</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&amp;代表行的结束</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">d代表删除</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">用//将3段代码隔开</p></div></li><li class=\"exp-content-list list-item-4\" style=\"margin: 1px 0px 0px 17px; padding: 45px 0px 0px 35px; display: block; position: relative; min-height: 31px; border-left-width: 2px; border-left-style: dotted; border-left-color: rgb(228, 228, 228);\"><div class=\"list-icon\" style=\"width: 32px; height: 32px; position: absolute; left: -18px; top: 43px; color: rgb(238, 255, 238); text-align: center; line-height: 32px; background-image: url(http://img.baidu.com/img/iknow/exp/global/step_ol_bg.png); font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 微软雅黑, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; visibility: hidden; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\"></div><div class=\"content-list-text\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 微软雅黑, arial, 宋体, sans-serif;\"><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">看吧，是不是删除了所有空白行了</p></div><div class=\"content-list-media\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 微软雅黑, arial, 宋体, sans-serif;\"><div class=\"content-list-image clearfix\" style=\"zoom: 1; position: relative; padding: 10px 0px;\"><a class=\"exp-image-wraper\" href=\"http://jingyan.baidu.com/album/a378c960911053b32928305b.html?picindex=3\" log=\"type:20150831,pos:enter_step,expGroup:G0\" target=\"_self\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(45, 100, 179); position: relative; display: block; float: left;\"><img class=\"exp-image-default\" alt=\"VIM删除空白行\" src=\"quiver-image-url/054153C06F7121746B1B953387DDA56B.png\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block;\" width=\"375\" height=\"285\"><span class=\"exp-album-enter-mask\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 0px; right: 0px; top: 0px; bottom: 0px; background-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); opacity: 0.1; cursor: pointer;\"></span><span class=\"enter-step-btn\" style=\"background-image: url(http://img.baidu.com/img/iknow/exp/article/show-step.png); width: 120px; height: 40px; position: absolute; top: 50%; left: 50%; margin-top: -20px; margin-left: -60px; line-height: 40px; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 22px; display: block; text-align: left; cursor: pointer; zoom: 1; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\">步骤阅读</span><div><br></div></a></div></div><div style=\"clear: both;\"></div></li></ol></div></div></div>"
    }
